      <body>
         <div type="address">
            <address>
               <addrLine>
                  <pb facs="MS-B-00005-B-000-00137"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Arthur Schnitzler</hi>
               </addrLine>
               <addrLine>
                  <rs ref="#pmb59" type="place">Wien IX</rs>
               </addrLine>
               <addrLine>
                  <rs ref="#pmb397" type="place">Frankgaſſe</rs> 1</addrLine>
            </address>
         </div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1">
            <opener>
               <dateline rend="right">
                  <pb facs="MS-B-00005-B-000-00136"/>
                  <date>29. 10.</date>
               </dateline>
               <salute>Lieber Arthur!</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>Ich glaube, <rs ref="#pmb10883" type="person">Berger</rs> iſt <anchor xml:id="K_L01186_1" type="commentary"/>noch hier<note xml:id="K_L01186_1h" type="commentary">Am <date>30. 10. 1901</date> kam <rs ref="#pmb10883" type="person">Berger</rs> zu <rs ref="#pmb2121" type="person">Schnitzler</rs>.</note>; Du
               kannſt es, da er Telephon hat, ſofort erfahren.</p>
            <p>– <rs ref="#pmb29853" type="work">
                  <hi rend="latintype">Gustl</hi>
               </rs> – <rs ref="#pmb2185" type="person">Guttmann</rs> iſt echt. Es gibt nur ein <rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs>, beſonders für Dichter.</p>
            <closer>Herzlichſt<lb/>Dein<lb/>
               <signed>HermannBahr</signed>
            </closer>
         </div>
      </body>
